SIMPLE: forget-me-not
RECORDS: 1

==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Forget-me-not
<hw>For*get"-me-not`</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[Cf. G.
<ets>vergissmeinnicht</ets>.]</ety> <fld>(Bot.)</fld> <def>A small
perennial herb, of the genus <gen>Myosotis</gen> (<spn>Myosotis
scorpiodes</spn>, <spn>Myosotis palustris</spn>, <spn>Myosotis
incespitosa</spn>, etc.), bearing a beautiful bright blue or white
flowers, and extensively considered the emblem of fidelity.</def>⟦br⟧
<syn><b>Syn. --</b> mouse ear, .</syn>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source> + <source>WordNet 1.5</source>]</p>

<p><note>⟦hand⟧ Formerly the name was given to the <spn>Ajuga
Cham⟦ae⟧pitus</spn>.</note>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Forgettable</ent>⟦br⟧
